  "text": "QTHs emit the light when an electric current flows through heated tungsten filament which surrounded by halogen gas. Because these filaments acted as resistors to the passage of electric current, heat was generated [CITATION_1] . Filters were used to restrict the light to the blue region required for composite polymerization [CITATION_2] .",
